  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="white_box_shadow"><img src="/media/13103738/3for2-offer-new.jpg" alt="Lapland3for2Offer" data-udi="umb://media/943c216a76d0438b95ed3916b86ed786" /></div>
<h2>3 for 2 on Lapland excursions - Save up to £92pp</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Book early to secure this offer </strong></li>
<li>Includes: full length husky ride, reindeer sleigh and snowmobile safari</li>
<li>Book via your <a rel="noopener" href="https://my.inghams.co.uk/login" target="_blank" title="My Booking">My Booking</a> portal (see how below) or call our team on 01483 945 237</li>
</ul>
<p>Make the most of Lapland and enjoy 3 for 2 on our exciting excursions:</p>
<p><strong>Snowmobile Safari</strong> - race across the arctic ice on your snowmobile as you chase the northern lights and take in the snow-covered forests and frozen lakes.</p>
<p><strong>Reindeer sleigh</strong> - Snuggle up together under a blanket on your own reindeer drawn sleigh. Let the reindeer meander through the beautiful landscape whilst you sit back and enjoy the views. </p>
<p><strong>Husky ride</strong> - Take part in this thrilling and traditional mode of transport out on the ice and snow. The huskies will glide you across stunning snow-laden pathways of Lapland. </p>
<p><em>*See T&amp;C's at the bottom of this page for more detail</em></p>
<h2>How to book your 3 for 2 excursion offer</h2>
<p>1 - Select the 'extras' tab on the check-out page:</p>
<p><img style="width: 500px; height: 182.08430913348946px;" src="/media/13104117/booking-step-1.jpg?width=500&amp;height=182.08430913348946" alt="BookingStep1" data-udi="umb://media/4af73b7fdcf84d219b63b16be2f5c700" /></p>
<p>2: Scroll down the page to Winter Excursions and Lapland Excursion offer:</p>
<p><img style="width: 500px; height: 136.77354709418836px;" src="/media/13104118/booking-step-2.jpg?width=500&amp;height=136.77354709418836" alt="BookingStep2" data-udi="umb://media/3c7578b88e064ddfaa63f3b1fdc438c4" /></p>
<p>3: Select your preferences and click confirm:</p>
<p><img style="width: 500px; height: 247.3684210526316px;" src="/media/13104119/booking-step-3.jpg?width=500&amp;height=247.3684210526316" alt="BookingStep3" data-udi="umb://media/73509b0e61934c50b00351b533a2f4c2" /></p>
<p>4: You will then see your selection has been added to your booking:</p>
<p><img style="width: 500px; height: 173.5611510791367px;" src="/media/13104120/booking-step-4.jpg?width=500&amp;height=173.5611510791367" alt="BookingStep4" data-udi="umb://media/97d32b8528ec4e57975ccdb47edb990a" /></p>
