<p>All three excursions are available in all of our Lapland resorts and by booking this offer you can save:</p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Levi</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13095233/inghams-lapland-adobestock_137614597.jpeg" alt="LeviResort" data-udi="umb://media/ba3823fbfa244e9696140ecf87c6f966" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Adult – save £90 </strong><br /><strong>Child – save £65</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c}" title="Levi" class="c-btn">View Levi resort</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Ylläs</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13095242/inghams-lapland-adobestock_288733450.jpeg" alt="YllasResort" data-udi="umb://media/56d10193110847028f24ae22b433f4f5" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Adult – save £90 </strong><br /><strong>Child – save £65</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c}" title="Yllas" class="c-btn">View Yllas resort</a></p>
</div>
</div>
