<p><img src="/media/13095243/inghams-lapland-adobestock_290274561.jpeg" alt="SaariselkaResort" data-udi="umb://media/0e6a75dca28a46749faeec7a69f2556e" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Adult – save £92 </strong><br /><strong>Child – save £65</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka" class="c-btn">View Saariselka resort</a></p>
