<h2 class="g12" style="text-align: left;">More about Lapland excursions:</h2>
<p>Inghams Lapland holidays have so much to offer, your week will full of exciting adventures. View all of our excursion options <a data-udi="umb://document/bda83b0ac78e4ae8aa3f5206e06059da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bda83b0ac78e4ae8aa3f5206e06059da}" title="Lapland Safaris &amp; Excursions">here</a>.</p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13095228/inghams-lapland-adobestock_124523338.jpeg" alt="SnowMobileExcursion" data-udi="umb://media/572de64a3a8248c1adfe9a48f03b7920" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Experience an exhilarating ride through the breath-taking arctic scenery </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/345a78d93ecb4821a7eb5c47c0382ee6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/345a78d93ecb4821a7eb5c47c0382ee6}#snowmobilesafari" class="c-btn">Snowmobile Safari</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13095229/inghams-lapland-adobestock_124472096.jpeg" alt="HuskyRideExcursion" data-udi="umb://media/dba0a753005244309c19b4f3afc9fda0" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">You and your team of huskies will weave through deep forest in the low winter sun</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/c2bd76aba5e94e7d95f0525095d2c4ec" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c2bd76aba5e94e7d95f0525095d2c4ec}#huskysafari" class="c-btn">Husky Rides</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13095236/inghams-lapland-adobestock_179437066.jpeg" alt="ReindeerRideExcursion" data-udi="umb://media/6d543bfd3f58420e9e3961f29b144bf6" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Snuggle under a blanket and ride in a reindeer sleigh through the snowy fells and forests</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/588530ae17cd46a6ad7121ad9991d719" href="/{localLink:umb://document/588530ae17cd46a6ad7121ad9991d719}#reindeersafari" class="c-btn">Reindeer Rides</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<h3 style="text-align: left;">Terms and Conditions</h3>
<p style="text-align: left;">This offer applies to new bookings. This offer is valid on 7 night holidays to Lapland in winter 2024/25 and 2025/26 while stocks last. See exclusions below.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Cancellation:</strong> If you choose to cancel or if you choose not to participate in an excursion for whatever reason, the supplier’s terms and conditions will apply. No refunds can be offered for ‘free’ excursions. In the event of cancellation of a qualifying excursion, the cost of the ‘free’ excursion will be deducted from any refund due.</p>
<h4 style="text-align: left;">Terms and Conditions: </h4>
<ul style="text-align: left;">
<ul>
<ul>
<li>Buy 2 excursions and get 1 free</li>
<li>Save £92 in Saariselkä, £90 in Levi &amp; £90 in Ylläs (savings based on adult prices)</li>
<li>Valid on 7-night holidays to Lapland winter 2024/25 &amp; 25/26 subject to availability</li>
<li>Lowest cost excursion is free, which is always snowmobiles</li>
<li>Full discount does not apply to single drivers – they will receive £90 discount only</li>
<li>Offer not applicable to infants aged 0 - 3 years</li>
<li>Excursion experiences and durations vary between resorts and dependent on weather conditions</li>
<li>Applicable to following excursions in:</li>
</ul>
</ul>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: left;">- Levi: 8km Husky Safari, Farm visit &amp; 3km Safari and 28km Snowmobile Safari</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">- Ylläs: 9km Husky Safari, Reindeer Farm visit &amp; 1.5km Safari and 25km Snowmobile Safari</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">- Saariselkä: 5km Husky Safari, Reindeer Discovery and 10-15km Snowmobile</p>
<ul style="text-align: left;">
<ul>
<ul>
<li>Excursion days and times will be advised on arrival in resort</li>
<li>Offer is subject to availability and may be withdrawn at any time</li>
<li>Not valid on Santa Breaks</li>
</ul>
</ul>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Excursion Information:</strong> Excursion descriptions and conditions apply as per brochure and website. Times and distances are approximate and may vary due to weather and other conditions. Husky and Reindeer Safaris child age is 4-12yrs. Children 0-3yrs are unable to book this offer. Snowmobile drivers must be 18yrs and bring a <strong>full, valid photographic driver's licence</strong> with them. Children must be 11yrs and over 140cm tall to ride as a passenger on a snowmobile safari. Children 10yrs and under or shorter than 140cm will be towed in a sled or pod behind a guide. Travel insurance is a condition of booking with us, and you should ensure that your chosen policy covers the activities that you plan to take part in during your holiday. Your policy should provide cover for your own personal and medical expenses, however individual policies will not cover damage to snowmobiles or skidoos and a compulsory excess will be payable directly to the supplier of the snowmobile/skidoo excursion. Snowmobiling single driver supplement is available for all resorts at an additional cost (18yrs+ only). All prices, offers and availability are correct at time of publication and are subject to change<em>.</em></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">*You must purchase the husky and reindeer safari in order to get the snowmobile safaris free. Savings based on adult prices. Save £85 in Levi, Ylläs and Saariselkä.  </p>
</div>
